OL,3,C'Chamber of abuse': Survivors recall
OL,4,Chorrors of life inside children's home
OL,6,FIt is a story which exposes how
OL,7,Fsociety's most vulnerable can be let
OL,8,Fdown and betrayed in the cruellest of
OL,9,Fways.
OL,11,FFor almost two decades hundreds of
OL,12,Fchildren were systematically sexually
OL,13,Fand physically abused inside Skircoat
OL,14,FLodge children's home, in Halifax, by
OL,15,Fthe very people who should have been
OL,16,Ftaking care of them.
OL,18,FToday two former bosses - Malcom
OL,19,FPhillips and Linda Brunning - were
OL,20,Ffound guilty of a string of attacks on
OL,21,Fchildren aged between six and 15.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/20
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1771883653
OL,3,C'Chamber of abuse': Survivors recall
OL,4,Chorrors of life inside children's home
OL,6,FBrunning will be sentenced at a later
OL,7,Fdate. Phillips, who was deemed unfit
OL,8,Fto stand trial, will avoid punishment.
OL,10,FFor many of those who suffered at
OL,11,Ftheir hands, the repercussions are
OL,12,Flifelong.
OL,14,FWhat happened at Skircoat Lodge?
OL,16,FSkircoat Lodge opened in the 1970s and
OL,17,Fclosed in 1995.
OL,19,FIt was set up as a residential
OL,20,Ftemporary home for children who were
OL,21,Fthe subject of care orders.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/20
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1771883653
OL,3,C'Chamber of abuse': Survivors recall
OL,4,Chorrors of life inside children's home
OL,6,FBut the court heard that it was run
OL,7,F"like a prison" by Malcolm Phillips.
OL,8,FAbuse went "unfettered and unreported
OL,9,Fagainst a backdrop of legitimacy" for
OL,10,Falmost two decades.
OL,12,FThe stories of those who were sent to
OL,13,FSkircoat Lodge are difficult to
OL,14,Fcomprehend.
OL,16,FKelly Lees was an 11-year-old who
OL,17,Fenjoyed school when she arrived at
OL,18,FSkircoat Lodge in 1992.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/20
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1771883653
OL,3,C'Chamber of abuse': Survivors recall
OL,4,Chorrors of life inside children's home
OL,6,FShe said: "They called it a children's
OL,7,Fhome. It was chamber. There were
OL,8,Fchildren being abused there on a daily
OL,9,Fbasis."
OL,11,FKelly said she became one of Phillips'
OL,12,Fchosen victims.
OL,14,F"I used to get called into his office
OL,15,Fto do my homework and there's where I
OL,16,Fwas sexually abused. I was scared, I
OL,17,Fwas petrified, we all were in there,"
OL,18,Fshe said.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/20
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1771883653
OL,3,C'Chamber of abuse': Survivors recall
OL,4,Chorrors of life inside children's home
OL,6,F"The more vulnerable that you were,
OL,7,Fthe more likely you were to be chosen.
OL,8,FThey owned us, there wasn't any care
OL,9,For love or nurture. There wasn't any
OL,10,Fstructure, there was abuse and abuse
OL,11,Fand abuse."
OL,13,FNow 44, Kelly says she is still
OL,14,Fhaunted by the screams of other
OL,15,Fchildren she heard during the night.
OL,17,F"The impact of that place is
OL,18,Fabsolutely shocking, there are a lot
OL,19,Fof people who aren't around, due to
OL,20,Foverdose or suicide," she said.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/20
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1771883653
OL,3,C'Chamber of abuse': Survivors recall
OL,4,Chorrors of life inside children's home
OL,6,FKaz Gray, another former resident, has
OL,7,Fwritten a blog about the "nightmare"
OL,8,Fshe endured at Skircoat Lodge.
OL,10,FShe attempted to run away several
OL,11,Ftimes but on each occasion was brought
OL,12,Fback by the police.
OL,14,F"I'd get found, taken back and beaten.
OL,15,FThe beatings got worse - they took
OL,16,Fyour shoes away to stop you running
OL,17,Foff again." she said.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/20
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1771883653
OL,3,C'Chamber of abuse': Survivors recall
OL,4,Chorrors of life inside children's home
OL,6,F"Once when I'd been returned by the
OL,7,Fpolice, Phillips frogmarched me back
OL,8,Fto my room. He slammed me against the
OL,9,Fwardrobe door and I felt my nose
OL,10,Fcrunch.
OL,12,F"I started crying when I saw the
OL,13,Fblood. I was 14. "
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/20
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1771883653
OL,3,C'Chamber of abuse': Survivors recall
OL,4,Chorrors of life inside children's home
OL,6,FKaz said some girls were invited to
OL,7,Fvideo nights with Malcolm Phillips and
OL,8,Fone would remain with him when the
OL,9,Fothers returned to their dormitory.
OL,10,FShe is thankful she wasn't one of them
OL,11,Fbut she finds it too difficult to talk
OL,12,Fabout the effect it had on those who
OL,13,Fwere.
OL,15,F"Most of the staff were terrified of
OL,16,Fhim, never mind the kids. He was a
OL,17,Fpeacock. He loved attention," she said.
OL,19,FLinda Brunning often physically
OL,20,Fassaulted her, too.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G8/20
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1771883653
OL,3,C'Chamber of abuse': Survivors recall
OL,4,Chorrors of life inside children's home
OL,6,F"She would pin me up against the wall,
OL,7,FI kicked her shins, she'd slap me just
OL,8,Fto warm me up and hand me over to
OL,9,FPhillips for another battering," she
OL,10,Fsaid.
OL,12,F"I saw one lad pinned on the floor by
OL,13,FBrunning, she sat across him and
OL,14,Fshouted at him. It was the same lad
OL,15,Fshe made eat his food off the floor
OL,16,Fone day - not off a plate on the
OL,17,Ffloor, off the floor."
OL,19,FKaz said that she and the other
OL,20,Fchildren had no-one to turn to.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G9/20
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36110
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1771883653
OL,3,C'Chamber of abuse': Survivors recall
OL,4,Chorrors of life inside children's home
OL,6,F"Social workers knew, the the staff
OL,7,Fknew, the police knew - who do you
OL,8,Ftell when everybody around you already
OL,9,Fknows?" she said.
OL,11,FChris Wild went to Skircoat Lodge at
OL,12,Fthe age of 12 when his previously
OL,13,Fhappy family life was shattered by the
OL,14,Fdeath of his father.
OL,16,FHe had become homeless and involved in
OL,17,Fcrime when he was sent to the home. He
OL,18,Fwrote "Damaged" - a book about his
OL,19,Fexperiences - and now campaigns for
OL,20,Fbetter safeguarding for children in
OL,21,Fcare.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G10/20
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36111
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1771883653
OL,3,C'Chamber of abuse': Survivors recall
OL,4,Chorrors of life inside children's home
OL,6,FChris says he was afraid from the
OL,7,Fmoment he stepped into Skircoat Lodge.
OL,9,F"There was an ominous silence about
OL,10,Fthe place, it smelled of bleach," he
OL,11,Fsaid.
OL,13,F"We couldn't talk and the staff ruled
OL,14,Fit with an iron fist, it was clear it
OL,15,Fwas a dangerous place. If you were
OL,16,Fwalking along the corridor they
OL,17,Fwouldn't think twice and tripping you
OL,18,Fup and smacking you round the head."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G11/20
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36112
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1771883653
OL,3,C'Chamber of abuse': Survivors recall
OL,4,Chorrors of life inside children's home
OL,6,FToday he describes himself as one of
OL,7,Fthe lucky ones because he was merely
OL,8,Fphysically, but not sexually, abused.
OL,10,FChris said he wrote the book because
OL,11,Fof his own experiences and to give
OL,12,Fother people a voice.
OL,14,F"Not enough change has been made in
OL,15,Fthe care system," he said. "Yes we
OL,16,Fhave regulators but we need stronger
OL,17,Flegislation to keep children safe.
OL,18,FSafeguarding as it stands isn't enough
OL,19,Fand doesn't stop children being abused
OL,20,Ftoday.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G12/20
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36113
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1771883653
OL,3,C'Chamber of abuse': Survivors recall
OL,4,Chorrors of life inside children's home
OL,6,FIf we don't have a reform of the care
OL,7,Fsystem the mistakes of the past will
OL,8,Fmake their way back into the care
OL,9,Fsystem we have today and more children
OL,10,Fwill suffer because of that."
OL,12,FInsight by Katie Oscroft
OL,14,FIt is incredible to think that
OL,15,Fhundreds of children were sent to this
OL,16,Fhome in a leafy suburb of Halifax and
OL,17,Ftreated so appallingly.
OL,19,FWhen they became desperate and tried
OL,20,Fto run away, they were brought back
OL,21,Fand punished.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G13/20
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36114
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1771883653
OL,3,C'Chamber of abuse': Survivors recall
OL,4,Chorrors of life inside children's home
OL,6,FThe people who spoke to me call
OL,7,Fthemselves "survivors". They also
OL,8,Fspeak about many who didn't - who took
OL,9,Ftheir own lives.
OL,11,FThose I interviewed are desperate to
OL,12,Fmake things better for others.
OL,14,FKelly wants to change the way people
OL,15,Fdamaged by experiences in care are
OL,16,Ftreated.
OL,18,FKaz writes a blog and through it she
OL,19,Fhas made contact with others who say
OL,20,Fsharing experiences has helped them.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G14/20
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36115
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1771883653
OL,3,C'Chamber of abuse': Survivors recall
OL,4,Chorrors of life inside children's home
OL,6,FChris campaigns to reform a system he
OL,7,Fsays is still letting vulnerable
OL,8,Fchildren down.
OL,10,FThey all believe that many more people
OL,11,Fwere complicit in the regime at
OL,12,FSkircoat Lodge and should be brought
OL,13,Fto justice. People who worked for
OL,14,Fagencies - like police and social
OL,15,Fservices - who should have been there
OL,16,Fto protect them.
OL,18,F"We were labelled bad children," Kelly
OL,19,Fsays.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G15/20
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36116
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1771883653
OL,3,C'Chamber of abuse': Survivors recall
OL,4,Chorrors of life inside children's home
OL,6,FThe convictions of Malcolm Phillips
OL,7,Fand Linda Brunning dispel that
OL,8,Fnarrative once and for all. But for
OL,9,Fthe survivors the conclusion of court
OL,10,Fproceedings is not the end of the
OL,11,Fstory.
OL,13,FIn 1995 police began Operation Screen,
OL,14,Fan investigation which saw Malcolm
OL,15,FPhillips jailed for seven years for a
OL,16,Fstring of sexual offences including
OL,17,Frape and indecent assault.
OL,19,FBut that was not the end of the matter.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G16/20
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36117
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1771883653
OL,3,C'Chamber of abuse': Survivors recall
OL,4,Chorrors of life inside children's home
OL,6,FProtests outside Calderdale Council -
OL,7,Fthe authority responsible for Skircoat
OL,8,FLodge - called for the case to be
OL,9,Freinvestigated.
OL,11,FThe current police investigation,
OL,12,FOperation Henway, began in 2017 after
OL,13,Fmore victims campaigned for their
OL,14,Fcases to be heard.
OL,16,FThat ultimately led to the latest
OL,17,Fcourt proceedings and justice for some
OL,18,Fof those who suffered at the hands of
OL,19,FPhillips and Brunning.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G17/20
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36118
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1771883653
OL,3,C'Chamber of abuse': Survivors recall
OL,4,Chorrors of life inside children's home
OL,6,FBut David Greenwood, a solicitor who
OL,7,Frepresents victims, has criticised
OL,8,FWest Yorkshire Police for the delay in
OL,9,Fcontinuing to investigate after
OL,10,FPhillips was first convicted.
OL,12,F"Its a shame that West Yorkshire
OL,13,FPolice didn't take this more
OL,14,Fseriously. perhaps they thought their
OL,15,Fjob was done after the first
OL,16,Finvestigation in 2001," he said.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G18/20
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36119
SC,0019
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1771883653
OL,3,C'Chamber of abuse': Survivors recall
OL,4,Chorrors of life inside children's home
OL,6,F"Remember this investigation only
OL,7,Fstarted again in 2017 and it is now
OL,8,F2026. A lot of people will be very
OL,9,Fdisappointed that Malcolm Phillips all
OL,10,Fbut escaped justice because this was
OL,11,Fsimply a trial of the facts in his
OL,12,Fcase."
OL,14,FMr Greenwood is calling for an inquiry
OL,15,Finto why the police failed to
OL,16,Finvestigate sooner and says there are
OL,17,Flikely to be many more victims whose
OL,18,Fcases have still not been heard.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G19/20
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36120
SC,0020
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1771883653
OL,3,C'Chamber of abuse': Survivors recall
OL,4,Chorrors of life inside children's home
OL,6,F"Skircoat Lodge was almost like a
OL,7,Fprison, children were treated like
OL,8,Fsecond class citizens, given
OL,9,Finadequate food and living under the
OL,10,Fthreat of physical and sexual
OL,11,Fviolence," he said.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G20/20
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
